*{NAME}
  tfmt - format text

*{SYNOPSIS}
  ${tfmt} [*{options}] *{FILE ...}

*{DESCRIPTION}
  ${tfmt} formats text according to a simple format specification.  See *{tfmt}(*{7}) for details.

  Supported options:
    *{--wrap=N}
      Word-wrap the output text at *{N} characters.  If this is not specified, the output text will not be pre-wrapped.

